# Unified scheduler — America/New_York
#
# Entry scans during market hours (Mon-Fri, 9am-4pm ET).
0 9-16 * * 1-5    quanterback scan
# Extra run 30 minutes after open.
30 9 * * 1-5      quanterback scan

# Position lifecycle tracker.
# Runs 24/7 because zombie-pending cleanup must clear stale orders
# regardless of market hours (else cap stays locked on weekends).
*/5 * * * *       quanterback track-positions
